:"2019-09-16T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"我突然之間諗到<br />\n會唔會係冇俾身分證嘅先會送去新屋嶺"},{"pid":"1d5341e3ce1361b2714ad1ec20bfd87e0adc9f17","tid":1575000,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f12f9015885a1ef76c46b0d9a18ff3dae2818206","tid":1575000,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"我突然之間諗到<br />\n會唔會係冇俾身分證嘅先會送去新屋嶺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"補充<br />\n否則我真係睇唔到個合法性喺邊"},{"pid":"0e941cd6725a20cb7ac55b2020d659c15f266970","tid":1575000,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"你訓左幾耐"},{"pid":"ad41dd47eb0a1ad92c88df2e6f4f4e85fb90182d","tid":1575000,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:30:24.000Z","msg":"犯法又點 搵邊個拉佢地?"},{"pid":"a2c64793d38b0745b8f6516ddb55011881690806","tid":1575000,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e941cd6725a20cb7ac55b2020d659c15f266970","tid":1575000,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"你訓左幾耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:42:22.000Z","msg":"佢都係想多個辦法禁止用新屋嶺姐"}]}